==English==

===Adjective===
'''yarak''' 
# ''(falconry):'' ''(derived from Persian)'' Superalert, hungry but not weak, and ready to hunt.

[[tr:yarak]]
English meaning of the Turkish word "Yarak" is penis or cock. Generally is considered to be vulgar but is a commonly used word in Turkish language. Sample sentences: 1) O adamin yaragini ilk kez bir kadinin amcigina sokarken gordum; sasirmistim. 2) Yaragi epeyce sertlesmisti onu son gordugumde. Keske amcigimin icine o yaragi sokabilseydi.